{"builtWith":"0.15.15","comments":[{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":"                               // hydrogen // optimize // submodular // online"},{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":" | Online Submodular Maximization via First-Order Regret Bounds."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Theoretical Foundation"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | This module implements the Harvey/Liaw/Soma (NeurIPS 2020) algorithm for"},{"LineComment":" | online submodular maximization with first-order regret bounds."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | **Key Result**: O(√(kT ln(n/k))) expected α-regret for monotone + matroid"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | The algorithm maintains a fractional solution x ∈ P(M) (matroid polytope)"},{"LineComment":" | and updates it via online gradient descent with Blackwell approachability."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Online Model"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | At each round t:"},{"LineComment":" | 1. Algorithm selects set Sₜ ∈ I (independent in matroid M)"},{"LineComment":" | 2. Adversary reveals submodular function fₜ"},{"LineComment":" | 3. Algorithm receives utility fₜ(Sₜ)"},{"LineComment":" | 4. Algorithm updates internal state"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | The adversary IS reality: fₜ is revealed by actual GPU execution."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Blackwell Approachability"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | The algorithm uses Blackwell's approachability theorem to convert"},{"LineComment":" | vector-valued payoffs into scalar regret bounds. This enables:"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - First-order regret: bounds depend on actual gains, not worst-case"},{"LineComment":" | - Adaptive learning rates: faster convergence when problem is \"easy\""},{"LineComment":" | - Anytime guarantees: valid regret bound at any stopping time"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## References"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - Harvey, Liaw, Soma. \"Improved Algorithms for Online Submodular"},{"LineComment":" |   Maximization via First-order Regret Bounds\" NeurIPS 2020"},{"LineComment":" | - Blackwell, D. \"An Analog of the Minimax Theorem for Vector Payoffs\""},{"LineComment":" |   Pacific J. Math. 6(1), 1-8 (1956)"},{"LineComment":" | - Si Salem et al. \"Online Submodular Maximization via Online Convex"},{"LineComment":" |   Optimization\" arXiv:2309.04339v4 (January 2024)"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Lean4 Proof Correspondence"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | This module implements algorithms proven correct in:"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - `proofs/Hydrogen/Optimize/Submodular/RAOCO.lean`"},{"LineComment":" |   - `raoco_reduction`: α-regret_T(P_X) ≤ α · regret_T(P_Y)"},{"LineComment":" |   - `wtp_matroid_raoco`: (1-1/e)-regret = O(√T) for WTP over matroids"},{"LineComment":" |   - `thresholdPotential`: Weighted threshold potential definition"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - `proofs/Hydrogen/Optimize/Submodular/ContinuousGreedy.lean`"},{"LineComment":" |   - `continuous_greedy_guarantee`: F(x_T) ≥ (1-(1-1/T)^T)·OPT"},{"LineComment":" |   - `full_pipeline_guarantee`: Rounding preserves approximation"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - `proofs/Hydrogen/Optimize/Submodular/Matroid.lean`"},{"LineComment":" |   - `Matroid`: Independence system axioms (I1, I2, I3)"},{"LineComment":" |   - `inPolytope`: Matroid polytope membership"},{"LineComment":" |   - `matroidRank`: Rank of full ground set"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - `proofs/Hydrogen/Optimize/Submodular/Core.lean`"},{"LineComment":" |   - `FractionalSolution`: coords ∈ [0,1]^V with proof obligations"},{"LineComment":" |   - `IsSubmodular`: Diminishing returns property"},{"LineComment":" |   - `multilinearExt`: Extension to continuous domain"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Type Correspondence"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | | PureScript                  | Lean                        | Theorem/Definition      |"},{"LineComment":" | |-----------------------------|-----------------------------|-------------------------|"},{"LineComment":" | | `FractionalSolution v`      | `FractionalSolution V`      | Core.lean:232           |"},{"LineComment":" | | `MatroidPolytope m v`       | `inPolytope M x`            | Matroid.lean:155        |"},{"LineComment":" | | `solutionGroundSetSize`     | `Fintype.card V`            | Matroid.lean:259        |"},{"LineComment":" | | `polytopeGroundSet`         | Ground set `V`              | Matroid.lean:158        |"},{"LineComment":" | | `OnlineState.solution`      | Fractional point in P(M)    | RAOCO.lean:258          |"},{"LineComment":" | | `RegretState.alpha`         | `α = (1-1/Δ)^Δ`             | RAOCO.lean:122          |"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Module Structure"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | This leader module re-exports from:"},{"LineComment":" | - `Online.Config`: Configuration and utility feedback"},{"LineComment":" | - `Online.Regret`: Regret tracking and first-order bounds"},{"LineComment":" | - `Online.Blackwell`: Blackwell approachability"},{"LineComment":" | - `Online.State`: Online algorithm state"},{"LineComment":" | - `Online.Algorithm`: Core algorithm and utilities"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Dependencies"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - Hydrogen.Optimize.Submodular.Types (core types)"},{"LineComment":" | - Hydrogen.Optimize.Submodular.Continuous (fractional solutions)"},{"LineComment":" | - Hydrogen.Math.Core (exp, log, sqrt)"}],"decls":[],"exports":[],"foreign":[],"imports":[{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[154,17],"start":[144,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Optimize","Submodular","Online","Algorithm"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[134,17],"start":[129,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Optimize","Submodular","Online","Blackwell"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[114,14],"start":[108,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Optimize","Submodular","Online","Config"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[126,14],"start":[117,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Optimize","Submodular","Online","Regret"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[141,13],"start":[137,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Optimize","Submodular","Online","State"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[154,17],"start":[94,1]}},"moduleName":["Prim"]}],"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Optimize","Submodular","Online"],"modulePath":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Optimize/Submodular/Online.purs","reExports":{"Hydrogen.Optimize.Submodular.Online.Algorithm":["getSolutionCoord","groundSetDimension","isWarmupPhase","onlineRound","onlineStep","polytopeGroundSet","runOnline","solutionFromCoords","solutionGroundSetSize"],"Hydrogen.Optimize.Submodular.Online.Blackwell":["BlackwellState","blackwellResponse","blackwellUpdate","mkBlackwellState"],"Hydrogen.Optimize.Submodular.Online.Config":["OnlineConfig","UtilityFeedback","defaultOnlineConfig","mkOnlineConfig","mkUtilityFeedback"],"Hydrogen.Optimize.Submodular.Online.Regret":["RegretState","adaptiveStepSize","currentRegret","firstOrderBound","isWithinBound","mkRegretState","regretBound","updateRegret"],"Hydrogen.Optimize.Submodular.Online.State":["OnlineState","mkOnlineState","resetOnlineState"]},"sourceSpan":{"end":[154,17],"start":[94,1]}}